title: Better search rankings seen key to eBays growth
text:
Better search rankings seen key to eBay's growth 
Reuters Friday 23rd October, 2015 
After a surprisingly strong quarter shorn of PayPal, further growth for eBay Inc will rest on its ability to make its website more visible to those searching for items to buy....
